Package fr.atis_lab.physicalworld

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DrawingPanel
    Custom JPanel to paint the PhysicalWorld and its PhysicalObject
    The DrawingPanel is a "window" on the world (it can show only a part of it)
    The scale determine the ratio between the simulated world and the painted world
    PhysicalWorld
    PhysicalWorld is a wrapper around JBox2D World, adding some walls and a PhysicalObject list
    PhysicalWorld use org.jbox2d.common.Vec2 for its coordinate
    Serializer  
    Sprite
    Sprite is their to allow painting capacities and unique name to JBox2D Bodies
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidPolygonException
    Exception raised if a wrong vertice list is passed to the PhysicalObject constructor
    InvalidSpriteNameException
    Exception raised if a Sprite name is already used by another object
    LockedWorldException
    Exception raised if you try to destroy an object during simulation step
    ObjectNameNotFoundException
    Exception raised if a object with a wrong name is searched
